over inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span data-cds="Icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="[content-visibility:auto] [contain-intrinsic-size:auto_400px] px-2 -mx-2 pb-8 -mb-8 print:[content-visibility:visible]"><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="contents"><div class="mb-1 mt-[var(--msg-gap,1.5rem)] group"><h2 data-find-omitted="" class="sr-only select-none">You said: Critical — will break on launch</h2><div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-1"><div data-user-message-bubble="true" class="group relative inline-flex gap-2 bg-bg-300 rounded-xl pl-2.5 py-[var(--msg-bubble-py,0.625rem)] break-words text-text-100 transition-all max-w-[75ch] flex-col !px-[var(--msg-bubble-px,1rem)] max-w-[85%]" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="flex flex-row gap-2 relative"><div class="flex-1"><div data-testid="user-message" class="font-large !font-user-message py-0.5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 relative [&amp;_ul]:!space-y-0 [&amp;_ol]:!space-y-0 [&amp;_ul]:pl-8 [&amp;_ol]:pl-8" style="max-height: 200px; overflow: hidden; position: relative;"><p class="whitespace-pre-wrap break-words">Critical — will break on launch
Payment
Razorpay SDK not loaded — pay button shows but no payment occurs
Add &lt;script src="<a href="https://checkout.razorpay.com/v1/checkout.js%22%3E" target="_blank" class="underline">https://checkout.razorpay.com/v1/checkout.js"&gt;</a> and add your key_id. Right now clicking Pay just generates an e-pass without charging anyone.
Mobile CSS
Hero, crowd grid, stays grid, place detail, admin panel have no mobile breakpoints
.hero has 80px padding (cuts off on phones), .cg is always 2-col (too tight on 320px), .pd-hg is 2-col grid (overlaps on mobile), .adm-layout has no mobile stack.
Fix before launch
Supabase
5 columns missing from DB schema
Add to traveller_scores: guest_name (text), phone_hint (text). Add to bookings: guest_phone (text), nights (int4), guests (int4). Without these, profile lookup shows "Name not on record".
PWA
manifest.json and icon-192.png referenced but missing
Both will 404. Either create manifest.json + icons, or remove the &lt;link rel="manifest"&gt; and apple-touch-icon tags.
SEO
og:image points to /og-image.jpg which doesn't exist
WhatsApp/Twitter link previews will show a broken image. Create a 1200×630px image and upload it, or remove the og:image tag.
iOS
Input font-size is 14px — iOS Safari auto-zooms on focus
Any input with font-size &lt; 16px triggers iOS zoom. Set .fi, .ai, .pi, .psel font-size to 16px (or add touch-action: manipulation).
Legal
No cookie consent banner
You load Plausible analytics. Under India's DPDP Act 2023 and GDPR (if serving EU visitors), you need a consent notice. A simple one-line banner with Accept/Decline is enough.
UX
No permit form error display — processPermit() silently fails
If permit validation fails or Supabase errors, nothing tells the user. Add an error div like the booking form has.
SEO
No sitemap.xml or robots.txt
Google won't crawl efficiently without these. A static sitemap.xml pointing to paharipath.in and a permissive robots.txt takes 10 minutes to create.
Working well
Auth
Admin login uses Supabase Auth — no hardcoded passwords
Secure. Session clears on page unload.
Booking
Rate limiting (3 attempts/10min), validation, eco pledge check all present
Crowd
Live crowd data from Supabase, 5-minute auto-refresh, admin override, 5 label tiers
Map
Leaflet map with 146 pins, sidebar, filters, Near Me, offline fallback
Admin
All 10 tabs working — dash, crowd, destinations, stays, bookings, eco, feedback, NGO, media, profiles
Traveller
Points system, 6 tiers, badges, e-pass, NGO activities, host feedback all wired up
Data
146 destinations with correct coordinates, vibes, altitude, best season, zone
Performance
Single HTML file, lazy-loaded images, no build step, CDN for Leaflet/Supabase
Nice to have (post-launch)
UX
Skeleton loading states for crowd/stays cards — content pops in abruptly on slow connections
Images
Unsplash placeholder images — swap to your own hosted photos before going commercial
A11Y
Only 9 aria- attributes across the whole site — add aria-label to icon buttons and form controls
Offline
Leaflet map tiles require internet. A service worker caching strategy would help on slow HP mountain connections.                                                              add these things</p><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-12 bg-gradient-to-t from-bg-300 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div></div><button class="pb-3 pt-1 text-xs text-text-500/80 hover:text-text-100 transition w-3/4 text-left rounded-lg">Show more</button></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><span class="text-text-500 text-xs flex items-center mr-2" id="base-ui-_r_1dr_">Jun 21</span><div class="flex items-center"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Retry" id="base-ui-_r_1dt_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span data-cds="Icon" aria-hidden="true" style="font-