<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">On the Vercel dashboard look for this exact flow:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Add New</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Project</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">On the next screen, scroll down to the <strong>bottom</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">You'll see a small link that says <strong>"Or deploy without a repository"</strong> or <strong>"Continue with template"</strong> — click the one about deploying without a repository</li>
