<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Download <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">PahariPath_v4_final.html</code></li>
