<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong><a class="underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current" href="https://paharipath-navy.vercel.app/">https://paharipath-navy.vercel.app</a></strong></p>
