msg-assistant-pb,0.75rem)]" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><h2 data-find-omitted="" class="sr-only select-none">Claude responded: You're in the wrong settings — that's GitHub project settings, not repository settings.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">You're in the wrong settings — that's GitHub project settings, not repository settings.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Go back to <strong>vercel.com</strong> → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath-navy</code> project → <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Git</strong> and check if it shows the repo connected there.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">To test auto-deploy simply:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>github.com/Sakshu237/paharipath</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code> file</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click pencil ✏️ edit icon</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Make any tiny change</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Commit changes</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Check Vercel — should auto deploy in 30 seconds</li>
</ol></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_2dv_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span><span data-cds="Icon" class="absolute inset-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="tr