<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Host dashboard (hosts need their own login to manage listings)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Reviews system (guests review stays after checkout)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">WhatsApp notification to host when booking happens</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Notify me feature ("alert me when Spiti crowd drops")</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Content gaps:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Real photos for stays (currently placeholders)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Real homestay listings (only 12 seeded stays)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">og:image banner for social sharing</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Business:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Razorpay KYC completion</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">First 5 homestay partner outreach</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Buy <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code> domain</li>
</ul>
