solute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span><span data-cds="Icon" class="absolute inset-0 transition-all opacity-0 scale-50" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;"></span></span></span></button><div class="flex items-center"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="[content-visibility:auto] [contain-intrinsic-size:auto_400px] px-2 -mx-2 pb-8 -mb-8 print:[content-visibility:visible]"><div data-test-render-count="2"><div class="group" style="height: auto; opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="contents"><div data-is-streaming="false" class="group relative relative pb-[var(--msg-assistant-pb,0.75rem)]" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><h2 data-find-omitted="" class="sr-only select-none">Claude responded: The domain was just bought so it won't appear in search yet — Google takes 2-4 weeks to index a new domain.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">The domain was just bought so it won't appear in search yet — Google takes 2-4 weeks to index a new domain.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">But let's connect it to Vercel right now so the site loads when someone types <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code>:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>vercel.com</strong> → <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath-navy</code> project</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Settings</strong> → <strong>Domains</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Add Domain</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Type <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code> → click <strong>Add</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Vercel will show you two DNS records — share them here or follow these steps in GoDaddy:</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>In GoDaddy:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>godaddy.com</strong> → My Products → DNS</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Find <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code> → click <strong>Manage DNS</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Add the records Vercel shows you</li>
</ol>
