<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">✅ All 9 fixes:</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Admin/Host login hidden:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Both buttons removed from footer</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Admin: type <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">pahari</code> anywhere on keyboard → opens admin</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Host: go to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in/#host</code> or triple-click the invisible footer zone</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Host can also access via <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in/#admin</code> for admin</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Traveller Profile System:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">🏔️ <strong>My Profile</strong> button added to navbar</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Travellers enter name + phone → profile loads from Supabase</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Shows tier, points, stats, badges, recent activity</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">New travellers can create a profile (name, phone, email, city)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Auto-fills booking form</strong> if profile is active — no re-typing name/phone</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Profile persists in localStorage between sessions</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Host Self-Registration:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">"Register as a Host" link on host login page</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Hosts fill in property details + set their own email + password</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Creates Supabase auth account + saves partner application</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">After email verification → they can login to host dashboard</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Map sidebar improved:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Live crowd progress bar per destination with color coding</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Explore</strong> button → opens place detail directly</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Book</strong> button → jumps straight to booking for that destination</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Much more actionable than before</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>One thing still needed from you:</strong><br>
