<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>vercel.com</strong> → click <strong>paharipath1</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look at the <strong>Overview</strong> tab</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Check if it says <strong>"Connected to GitHub"</strong> and shows <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Sakshu237/paharipath</code></li>
