ponded: Good catch.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Good catch. That's a data accuracy issue — the coordinates in our <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">ALL</code> array are approximate, not exact GPS coordinates.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>The fix has two parts:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Part 1 — Fix Masroor temple coordinates</strong><br>
The correct coordinates for Masroor Rock Cut Temple are:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Lat: <strong>32.0407</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Lng: <strong>76.5647</strong></li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Part 2 — All 146 places need verified coordinates</strong><br>
This is the real problem. Many places in the <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">ALL</code> array have rough district-center coordinates, not exact location coordinates. This means pins show up in the wrong spot.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>How to fix all 146:</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">I can cross-reference each place name against known coordinates and update them. But it takes careful work — I need to check each one.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Want me to:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Fix Masroor now as a quick fix</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Then do a full coordinate audit of all 146 places and give you an updated file with verified coordinates</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">This will make the map actually useful for navigation — pins land exactly where the place is, not somewhere in the district.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Should I start the full coordinate fix now? It's important to do before building the POI system because accurate base coordinates are the foundation everything else depends on.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_2t3_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1