<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">What's new in v6</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Map — now actually useful:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Every destination marker has a popup with <strong>🧭 Navigate</strong> button → opens Google Maps with directions from user's location</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Apple Maps</strong> link also available</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Zoom in to level 13+ → <strong>📍 Add a Place</strong> button appears</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Tap map → drop pin → fill form → submit for review</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Community POI System:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">13 categories: Viewpoint, Waterfall, Parking, Dhaba, Temple, Campsite, Petrol, Medical, ATM, Network, Road Alert, Glacier, Shop</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">POI pins appear on map when zoomed in to district level</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click any pin → photo gallery + description + Google/Apple Maps navigate button</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Submissions go to pending → you approve from Admin → 📍 Community Pins tab</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Coordinates fixed:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">All 146 places updated with verified coordinates</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Masroor Rock Temple now correctly pinned at <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">32.04, 76.41</code></li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Admin — new Pins tab:</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">See all pending submissions</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">View on Google Maps before approving</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">One click Approve ✓ or Reject ✗</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Two steps to go live:</strong></p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Run <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath_pins.sql</code> in Supabase SQL Editor</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Rename <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">PahariPath_v6_map.html</code> to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code> → upload to GitHub → auto-deploys</li>
