-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Done. Here's what the new forecast looks like:</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">New Plan My Journey — Crowd Forecast</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>4-Week Summary Cards</strong> (top row)</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">This Week / Next Week / Week 3 / Week 4</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Each shows average crowd % with color + emoji</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✓ BEST WEEK badge on the quietest week</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click any card → auto-fills date and reruns forecast</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Week-by-Week Breakdown</strong> (below cards)</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Each week shows a mini bar chart — Mon to Sun</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Bar height = crowd level, color = green/amber/red</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Shows weather for that week (monsoon, snow, clear etc)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Shows ✅ Best day and ⚠️ Avoid day with specific dates</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>30-Day Calendar Grid</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Full month view, each day colored by crowd level</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click any day → instantly updates forecast for that date</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Today highlighted with white border</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Selected date shown in white</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">So now a traveller sees the whole picture instantly — not just one date, but which week, which day of that week is best to go.</p>
