<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>1. Place Detail Modal → 📅 Forecast tab</strong><br>
Click any destination card → open place detail → click <strong>📅 Forecast</strong> tab</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Shows:</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">4 week summary cards with crowd % and color</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">✓ BEST WEEK highlighted in green</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Bar chart for each week (Mon–Sun) with crowd bars</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Best day and worst day per week with specific dates</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Weather for each week (monsoon, snow, clear etc)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Green banner at bottom: "Best time to visit [Place]"</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click any week card → jumps to Plan My Journey with that week and place pre-selected</li>
</ul>
