single keystroke/selection.</h2><div class="font-claude-response relative leading-[1.65rem] [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:bg-bg-000/50 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-0.5 [&amp;_pre&gt;div]:border-border-400 [&amp;_.ignore-pre-bg&gt;div]:bg-transparent [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.standard-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pl-2 [&amp;_.progressive-markdown_:is(p,blockquote,ul,ol,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6)]:pr-8"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">That's because <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">runFC</code> is now <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">async</code> and it's waiting for a Supabase call (<code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">place_itineraries</code>) on every single keystroke/selection. Fix is simple — show a loading state immediately, and cache the itinerary so it only fetches once per place:</p></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div data-find-omitted="" class="contents"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-[var(--msg-pill-py,0.375rem)]"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Cache itinerary per place to avoid repeated Supabase calls</span><span class="inline-flex -rotate-90 shrink-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover/status:opacity-100 group-focus-visible/status:opacity-100"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Cache itinerary per place to avoid repeated Supabase calls</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Now show instant results while the itinerary loads in background:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div data-find-omitted="" class="contents"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-[var(--msg-pill-py,0.375rem)]"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Show instant skeleton while itinerary loads</span><span class="inline-flex -rotate-90 shrink-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover/status:opacity-100 group-focus-visible/status:opacity-100"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Show instant skeleton while itinerary loads</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Also pre-fetch itinerary when user selects a place, before they click Get Forecast:</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="mt-4"><div class="grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 min-w-0"><div data-find-omitted="" class="contents"><div class="min-w-0 pl-2 py-[var(--msg-pill-py,0.375rem)]"><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="group/status flex items-center gap-2 py-1 text-sm transition-colors cursor-pointer text-left text-text-500 hover:text-text-300 flex-1 min-w-0" aria-expanded="false"><div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 min-w-0" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="truncate font-base">Ran 5 commands, read a file</span><span class="inline-flex -rotate-90 shrink-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200 group-hover/status:opacity-100 group-focus-visible/status:opacity-100"><div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;"><path d="M14.128 7.165a.502.502 0 0 1 .744.67l-4.5 5-.078.07a.5.5 0 0 1-.666-.07l-4.5-5-.06-.082a.501.501 0 0 1 .729-.656l.075.068L10 11.752z"></path></svg></div></span></div></button></div><span class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite">Ran 5 commands, read a file</span><div class="grid transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-300 ease-out" style="grid-template-rows: 0fr;"><div class="overflow-hidden min-w-0"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row-start-2 col-start-1 relative grid grid-rows-[auto_auto] isolate min-w-0"><div class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Three speed fixes applied:</p>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Itinerary cached per place</strong> — first time you select Spiti it fetches from Supabase, every time after that it's instant from memory. No repeated network calls.</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Pre-fetch on place select</strong> — the moment you pick a destination from the dropdown, it silently fetches the itinerary in the background. By the time you click Get Forecast, it's already loaded.</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Instant skeleton</strong> — forecast cards and weather show immediately. Itinerary shows "⏳ Loading itinerary…" for a split second then fills in — feels fast even if the network is slow.</li>
</ol>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Upload to GitHub → auto-deploys.</p></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 py-2"><div class="group/artifact-block relative flex text-left font-ui rounded-lg overflow-hidden border-0.5 transition duration-300 w-full hover:bg-bg-000/50 px-4 border-border-300 hover:border-border-200"><button type="button" class="absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer rounded-[inherit] focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-inset focus-visible:ring-accent-200" aria-label="View Paharipath v6 map"></button><div class="artifact-block-cell flex flex-1 align-start justify-between w-full"><div class="flex flex-1 gap-2 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-end w-[68px] relative shrink-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"><div class="absolute right-2 flex flex-1 overflow-hidden w-[52px] h-[71px] rounded-t-lg border-0.5 border-border-200 select-none scale-[1] group-hover/artifact-block:scale-[1.035] -rotate-[0.1rad] group-hover/artifact-block:-rotate-[0.065rad] duration-300 ease-out group-hover/artifact-block:duration-400 group-hover/artifact-block:ease-[cubic-bezier(0,0.9,0.5,1.35)] transition-transform backface-hidden will-change-transform translate-y-[19%] bg-gradient-to-b from-bg-000 to-bg-000/0 pt-4 items-start justify-center h-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 256 256" class="text-text-500"><path d="M67.84,92.61,25.37,128l42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,1-7.68,9.22l-48-40a6,6,0,0,1,0-9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,1,7.68,9.22Zm176,30.78-48-40a6,6,0,1,0-7.68,9.22L230.63,128l-42.47,35.39a6,6,0,1,0,7.68,9.22l48-40a6,6,0,0,0,0-9.22Zm-81.79-89A6,6,0,0,0,154.36,38l-64,176A6,6,0,0,0,94,221.64a6.15,6.15,0,0,0,2,.36,6,6,0,0,0,5.64-3.95l64-176A6,6,0,0,0,162.05,34.36Z"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-1 py-4 min-w-0 flex-1"><div class="leading-tight text-sm line-clamp-1">Paharipath v6 map</div><div class="text-xs line-clamp-1 text-text-400 opaci