<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Login</strong> with your user ID and password</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">After login you'll see a <strong>Dashboard</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Look for <strong>"New Application"</strong> or <strong>"Apply for License"</strong></li>
