<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">App shell (HTML, CSS, Leaflet) cached for instant load</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>3. OSRM routing on our own map</strong></p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
