<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">✅ What's done really well</h4>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Title tag</strong> — "PahariPath — Discover Real Himachal Pradesh" — clear, branded, keyword-rich</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Meta description</strong> — mentions 146+ destinations, live crowd tracking, direct booking — compelling and specific</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Keywords</strong> — covers Spiti, Parvati, Kinnaur, Tirthan, homestays, responsible travel — good long-tail coverage</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>OG tags</strong> — Twitter card, OG image, locale all set up for social sharing</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Geo tags</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">geo.placename</code> and <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">geo.region</code> correctly set to Himachal Pradesh</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Google site verification</strong> — already added, meaning Search Console is connected ✓</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><strong>Robots tag</strong> — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index, follow, max-snippet:-1</code> is exactly right for full visibility</li>
</ul>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">This is genuinely solid, better than most small travel sites.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">🔴 One critical issue</h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">Map needs internet — OpenStreetMap tiles require a connection. Connect to Wi-Fi and reload to see the full interactive map.</code></strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">This message is showing even though you have internet. Something's broken in the map's connectivity check. This is a real bug a visitor will hit immediately.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">🟡 Smaller things</h4>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">og:image</code> still points to <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">/og-image.jpg</code> which likely doesn't exist yet — check if it 404s when shared on WhatsApp</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">No actual stays showing — confirmed earlier this is expected, data comes later</li>
</ul>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">Want me to fix the map's false "needs internet" error right now? That's the one thing actively breaking the user experience.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-message-action-bar="" class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 pointer-coarse:opacity-100 transition"><div class="text-text-300"><div role="toolbar" aria-label="Message actions" class="text-text-300 flex select-none items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none cursor-[var(--cds-cursor-interactive)] aria-disabled:cursor-default data-[disabled]:cursor-default border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0 !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copy" data-testid="action-bar-copy" id="base-ui-_r_3l8_" tabindex="0"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; ali