<h3 class="text-text-100 mt-3 -mb-1 text-[1.125rem] font-bold">🔴 Still Need To Do</h3>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">1. Submit sitemap to Google Search Console</h4>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>search.google.com/search-console</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Select your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code> property</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Left menu → <strong>Sitemaps</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Enter <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sitemap.xml</code> → Submit</li>
</ol>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">2. Create <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">og-image.jpg</code></h4>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal">This is the banner image shown when someone shares your link on WhatsApp/Facebook/Twitter.</p>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Size: <strong>1200×630px</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Make on Canva — search "Open Graph image" template</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Include: PahariPath logo + a beautiful HP mountain photo + tagline</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Upload to GitHub root (same folder as <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">index.html</code>)</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">3. Create PWA icons</h4>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">icon-192.png</code> and <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">icon-512.png</code> — your logo, square format</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Upload to GitHub root</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">4. Request indexing manually (speeds things up)</h4>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Search Console → <strong>URL Inspection</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Enter <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">https://paharipath.in</code></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Click <strong>Request Indexing</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Do this for a few key pages once you have more content</li>
</ol>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">5. Backlinks (longer term, builds authority)</h4>
<ul class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Get listed on HP Tourism's website</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Get mentioned in travel blogs (reach out to bloggers)</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Share on Reddit r/IndiaTravel, r/himachalpradesh</li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Instagram bio link</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="text-text-100 mt-2 -mb-1 text-base font-bold">6. Page speed check</h4>
<ol class="[li_&amp;]:mb-0 [li_&amp;]:mt-1 [li_&amp;]:gap-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-decimal flex flex-col gap-1 pl-8 mb-3">
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Go to <strong>pagespeed.web.dev</strong></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Enter <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">paharipath.in</code></li>
<li class="font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2">Fix any red flags it shows (usually image sizes)</li>
</ol>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal"><strong>Most urgent right now:</strong> Submit your sitemap to Search Console (step 1) — takes 2 minutes and tells Google to actually crawl your site. Without this step, Google may take much longer to discover you.</p>
